    public static final class AuditRecordsTypes.OperationType
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, com.vmware.vapi.bindings.StaticStructure
    The OperationType class contains constant fields used to represent all possible config manager operations. This class was added in vSphere API 8.0.2.0.
